The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Tuesday, May 06, 2003 				 George abused
																								New Delhi, May 5 (PTI): Defence minister George Fernandes was in for a rude shock this morning when a person abused him over telephone at his residence.																								Police later traced the call to the Wazirpur industrial area in north Delhi and detained the caller identified as Gyanand Kumar Akhilesh. The caller, a native of Fernandes former parliamentary constituency Muzaffarpur in Bihar, is a guard at a factory in the Wazirpur area. 																								Akhilesh is being questioned by the police and security agencies.
